<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>mcstructure NBT Editor v18</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117;
    --panel: #161b22;
    --panel2: #1c2128;
    --border: #30363d;
    --text: #e6edf3;
    --text-dim: #8b949e;
    --accent: #58a6ff;
    --accent-dim: #1f6feb;
    --green: #3fb950;
    --red: #f85149;
    --yellow: #d29922;
    --purple: #bc8cff;
    --orange: #ffa657;
    --mono: 'SF Mono', 'Consolas', 'Menlo', monospace;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .wrap {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px 16px 80px;
  }
  header { padding: 8px 0 20px; }
  header h1 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 4px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  header p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 13px; }

  /* Tabs */
  .tabs {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .tab-btn {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-bottom: -1px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
    flex: 0 0 calc(25% - 2px);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

  /* Drop zone */
  .drop {
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 28px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 140px;
    white-space: normal;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .drop:hover, .drop.drag { border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(88,166,255,0.05); }
  .drop input { display: none; }
  .drop-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; opacity: 0.6; }
  .drop-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .drop-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); }

  .filebar {
    display: none; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 14px; padding: 10px 12px;
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px;
  }
  .filebar.show { display: flex; }
  .filebar .name { font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--accent); }
  .filebar .meta { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px; }
  .filebar button { background: none; border: none; color: var(--text-dim); cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; padding: 4px 8px; }
  .filebar button:hover { color: var(--text); }

  #status { margin-top: 12px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); display: none; }
  #status.show { display: block; }
  #status.error { color: var(--red); }

  #results { margin-top: 20px; }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-dim); margin: 24px 0 10px; font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Cards */
  .card {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .card-head {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .card-head .item-name { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); }
  .card-head .item-loc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); }

  .ench-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    padding: 8px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .ench-row:first-of-type { border-top: none; padding-top: 0; }
  .ench-id { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); width: 90px; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1.4; }
  .ench-name { font-size: 13px; flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .ench-lvl-input {
    width: 80px; background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 13px;
    padding: 6px 8px; border-radius: 6px; text-align: right;
  }
  .ench-lvl-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); }

  /* Delete enchant button */
  .del-ench-btn {
    background: none; border: none; color: var(--text-dim); cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 15px; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1;
    transition: color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  .del-ench-btn:hover { color: var(--red); background: rgba(248,81,73,0.1); }

  /* Add enchantment */
  .add-ench-bar {
    margin-top: 10px; padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center;
  }
  .add-ench-bar .ench-id-input {
    width: 80px; background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 13px;
    padding: 6px 8px; border-radius: 6px; text-align: center;
  }
  .add-ench-bar .ench-id-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); }
  .add-ench-bar .ench-id-label {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .add-ench-bar .ench-name-preview {
    flex: 1; min-width: 100px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: italic; padding: 6px 4px;
  }
  .add-ench-btn {
    background: rgba(88,166,255,0.1); border: 1px solid var(--accent-dim);
    color: var(--accent); font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .add-ench-btn:hover { background: rgba(88,166,255,0.2); }

  .ench-quickpick-wrap {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 6px; margin: 8px 0 0;
  }
  .ench-quickpick-chip {
    background: rgba(188,140,255,0.1); border: 1px solid var(--purple);
    color: var(--purple); font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 9px;
    border-radius: 999px; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap;
    font-family: var(--mono); text-align: center; overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  .ench-quickpick-chip:hover { background: rgba(188,140,255,0.22); }

  /* Toolbar */
  .toolbar {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .toolbar input {
    flex: 1; min-width: 120px; background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 13px; padding: 9px 10px; border-radius: 7px;
  }
  .btn {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text);
    font-size: 13px; padding: 9px 14px; border-radius: 7px; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .btn:hover { border-color: var(--text-dim); }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--accent-dim); border-color: var(--accent-dim); color: #fff; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); }

  /* Download bar */
  .download-bar {
    display: none; margin-top: 20px; padding: 16px;
    background: rgba(63,185,80,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(63,185,80,0.35);
    border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;
  }
  .download-bar.show { display: block; }
  .download-bar p { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--green); }
  .download-btn {
    background: var(--green); color: #0d1117; border: none; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 7px; cursor: pointer;
  }
  .download-btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

  .empty { text-align: center; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 13px; padding: 30px 10px; }
  .add-item-panel .card { background: var(--panel); }
  .badge-enchanted { font-size:10px; background:rgba(88,166,255,0.15); color:var(--accent);
    border:1px solid var(--accent-dim); border-radius:4px; padding:1px 6px; margin-left:6px; vertical-align:middle; }
  .badge-plain { font-size:10px; background:rgba(139,148,158,0.1); color:var(--text-dim);
    border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:4px; padding:1px 6px; margin-left:6px; vertical-align:middle; }

  /* ===== NBT TREE VIEW ===== */
  #treePanel { margin-top: 20px; }
  .tree-container {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: auto; max-height: 600px; overflow-y: auto;
  }
  .tree-node { white-space: nowrap; }
  .tree-toggle {
    cursor: pointer; user-select: none;
    display: inline-block; width: 16px; text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 10px;
  }
  .tree-key { color: var(--accent); }
  .tree-type { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 10px; margin: 0 4px; }
  .tree-val-str { color: var(--green); }
  .tree-val-num { color: var(--orange); }
  .tree-val-byte { color: var(--yellow); }
  .tree-val-tag { color: var(--purple); }
  .tree-children { margin-left: 18px; border-left: 1px solid var(--border); padding-left: 8px; }
  .tree-children.collapsed { display: none; }
  .tree-summary { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 11px; }

  /* ===== JSON VIEW ===== */
  #jsonPanel { margin-top: 20px; }
  .json-toolbar {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .json-toolbar input {
    flex: 1; min-width: 180px; background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 7px;
  }
  .json-toolbar input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--accent); }
  .json-box {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: auto; max-height: 600px; overflow-y: auto;
    white-space: pre;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .json-box .jk { color: var(--accent); }
  .json-box .js { color: var(--green); }
  .json-box .jn { color: var(--orange); }
  .json-box .jb { color: var(--yellow); }
  .json-box .jp { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .json-search-match { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.35); border-radius: 2px; }
  .copy-btn {
    background: var(--panel2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px; padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .copy-btn:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--text-dim); }
  .copy-btn.copied { color: var(--green); border-color: var(--green); }
  .json-stats { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); }
</style>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jszip/3.10.1/jszip.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <header>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div>
        <h1>mcstructure NBT Editor</h1>
        <p>Edit, add or remove enchantments · Browse NBT tree · View raw JSON — all in your browser.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px;padding-top:2px;">
        <span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);white-space:nowrap;">Enchant ID versiyasi:</span>
        <div style="display:flex;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;overflow:hidden;">
          <button id="btnOldVer" style="background:var(--panel2);color:var(--text-dim);border:none;font-size:12px;padding:6px 13px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:600;">Old</button>
          <button id="btnNewVer" style="background:var(--accent-dim);color:#fff;border:none;font-size:12px;padding:6px 13px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:600;border-left:1px solid var(--border);">New</button>
        </div>
        <span id="versionLabel" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--green);">1.21 – 1.26.x</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <label class="drop" id="dropZone">
    <input type="file" id="fileInput" accept=".mcstructure">
    <div class="drop-icon">📦</div>
    <div class="drop-text">Tap to choose a .mcstructure file</div>
    <div class="drop-sub">or drag and drop it here</div>
  </label>

  <!-- World yuklash -->
  <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:10px;">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="worldFolderBtn" style="flex:1;">🌍 World papkasini yuklash</button>
    <button class="btn" id="structureExportBtn" style="flex:1;">📂 .ldb fayllar tanlash</button>
  </div>
  <input type="file" id="worldFolderInput" webkitdirectory multiple style="display:none">
  <input type="file" id="structureExportInput" accept=".ldb" multiple style="display:none">

  <!-- World structure ro'yxati -->
  <div id="worldPanel" style="display:none;margin-top:14px;">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <span id="worldInfo" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-dim);flex:1;"></span>
      <input type="text" id="structureSearch" placeholder="🔍 Qidirish..." 
        style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:6px;width:200px;">
    </div>
    <!-- Checkboxlar bilan ro'yxat -->
    <div id="structureCheckList" style="max-height:320px;overflow-y:auto;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:8px;margin-bottom:10px;"></div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <button class="btn" id="selectAllBtn">☑ Hammasini tanlash</button>
      <button class="btn" id="selectNoneBtn">☐ Bekor qilish</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" id="exportSelectedBtn" style="flex:1;">⬇ Tanlanganllarni export (.mcpack)</button>
      <button class="btn" id="exportEachBtn">📦 Har birini alohida .mcstructure</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="structureExportStatus" style="margin-top:10px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-dim);"></div>
  <div id="structureExportResults"></div>

  <div class="filebar" id="fileBar">
    <div>
      <div class="name" id="fileName"></div>
      <div class="meta" id="fileMeta"></div>
    </div>
    <button id="clearBtn">Remove</button>
  </div>

  <div id="status"></div>

  <!-- TABS -->
  <div class="tabs" id="tabBar" style="display:none; margin-top:20px;">
    <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="enchants">📥 Import</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="enchlist">📜 Enchant List</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="containers">📦 Containers</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="trade">🧑‍🌾 Trade</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="entities">🧟 Entities</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="tree">🌲 NBT Tree</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="json">{ } Raw JSON</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="cmdblock">⚙ Command Block</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="spawner">🐣 Spawner</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="viewer3d">🧱 3D Viewer</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="export">📤 Eksport</button>
  </div>

  <!-- TAB: Enchantments -->
  <div id="tab-enchants">
    <div id="results"></div>
    <div class="toolbar" id="toolbar" style="display:none;">
      <input type="number" id="bulkValue" placeholder="Set all levels to…">
      <button class="btn" id="applyAllBtn">Apply to all</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Add new item panel -->
    <div class="add-item-panel" id="addItemPanel" style="display:none;">
      <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">➕ Add new item to structure</div>
      <div class="card">
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim);white-space:nowrap;">Qaysi containerga:</span>
          <select id="newItemContainerSel"
            style="flex:1;min-width:180px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:6px;"></select>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim);white-space:nowrap;">Item name:</span>
          <input type="text" id="newItemName" placeholder="diamond_sword  yoki  mymod:item"
            style="flex:1;min-width:180px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:6px;">
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim);white-space:nowrap;">Slot:</span>
          <input type="number" id="newItemSlot" placeholder="auto" min="0" max="53"
            style="width:60px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:7px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;">
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim);white-space:nowrap;">Count:</span>
          <input type="number" id="newItemCount" value="1" min="1" max="64"
            style="width:60px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:7px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;">
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim);white-space:nowrap;" title="Data/Damage qiymati — variantlar uchun, /give bilan stack mos kelishi uchun">Data:</span>
          <input type="number" id="newItemData" value="0" min="0"
            style="width:60px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:7px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;">
          <button class="btn btn-primary" id="addItemBtn">+ Add item</button>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);">Yuqorida qaysi container (sandiq, barrel, shulker — ichkisi ham) tanlangan bo'lsa, item shu containerga qo'shiladi. Keyin yuqoridan enchantment qo'shishingiz mumkin.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TAB: Enchant List -->
  <div id="tab-enchlist" style="display:none;">
    <div style="margin-top:20px;">
      <div class="section-title">📜 Shaxsiy Enchant List</div>
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.5;">
          .txt fayl yuklang. Ikki format qo'llab-quvvatlanadi: <b>yangi</b> — <code>id:strId daraja</code>
          (masalan <code>9:protection 3</code>, eksportda shu format ishlatiladi) yoki <b>eski</b> — faqat nom
          (masalan <code>Sharpness</code> yoki <code>Sharpness "5"</code>). Faylning <b>nomi</b> (masalan
          <code>sword.txt</code> → <b>sword</b>) ro'yxatda alohida list sifatida chiqadi. Shu listga bosilganda —
          ICHIDAGI barcha enchant'lar bir vaqtning o'zida tanlangan itemga qo'shiladi. Enchantments va Containers
          tablarida shu listlar tugma (chip) sifatida ko'rinadi.
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
          <label class="btn" id="enchListUploadLabel" style="cursor:pointer;">
            📁 .txt yuklash
            <input type="file" id="enchListFileInput" accept=".txt" style="display:none;">
          </label>
          <input type="text" id="enchListManualInput" placeholder='Yoki qo&#39;lda: Sharpness yoki Sharpness "5", Smite "3"'
            style="flex:1;min-width:180px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:6px;">
          <button class="btn btn-primary" id="enchListAddManualBtn">+ Yangi list sifatida qo'sh</button>
          <button class="btn" id="enchListClearBtn" style="color:var(--red);">🗑 Hammasini tozalash</button>
        </div>
        <div id="enchListStatus" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);"></div>
      </div>
      <div id="enchListItems"><div class="empty">
